### ═══════════════════════════════════════════
### CUSTOMERS
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════

### Get all customers
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/customers

###

### Get a single customer
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/customers/1

###

### Create a customer
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/customers
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customer_name": "Max Mustermann",
  "email": "max.mustermann@example.com",
  "phone": "+43 664 1234567",
  "address_id": 1
}

###

### Update a customer
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/customers/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "newemail@example.com"
}

###

### Delete a customer
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/customers/1


### ═══════════════════════════════════════════
### EMPLOYEES
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════

### Get all employees
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/employees

###

### Get a single employee
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/employees/1

###

### Create an employee
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/employees
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "employee_name": "Anna Bauer",
  "employee_username": "abauer",
  "employee_password": "securepassword123"
}

###

### Delete an employee
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/employees/1


### ═══════════════════════════════════════════
### RENTALS
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════

### Get all rentals
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/rentals

###

### Get a single rental
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/rentals/1

###

### Create a rental
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/rentals
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "rental_date": "2026-04-13",
  "required_date": "2026-05-13",
  "customer_id": 1,
  "employee_id": 1,
  "book_copy_id": 1
}

###

### Delete a rental
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/rentals/1


